Ever been stuck in a long online meeting on google meet while wfh.  We all have. Those meetings where only few parts concern you and you still have to pay attention to the whole thing.
With this extension, you can enter upto 5 keywords and get a chrome notification whenever any of these keywords get mentioned.

Prerequisites :
* Keep captions of the meet on.
* Switch on chrome notifications.
